headline: 1 Value Stock with Competitive Advantages and 2 We Ignore
summary: Value investing has created more billionaires than any other strategy, like Warren Buffett, who built his fortune by purchasing wonderful businesses at reasonable prices. But these hidden gems are few and far between - many stocks that appear cheap often stay that way because they face structural issues.

headline: CDW (CDW): Assessing Valuation After New AWS AI Recognition and Cloud Solutions Launch
summary: CDW (CDW) is back on traders radar after its Mission subsidiary rolled out six integrated cloud solutions on AWS Marketplace and secured AWS Agentic AI Specialization, sharpening the companys positioning in cloud, security, and autonomous AI services. See our latest analysis for CDW. Even with Mission’s AWS wins sharpening the growth story, CDW’s 1 year total shareholder return of negative 17.68 percent and 3 month share price return of negative 14.81 percent show momentum has cooled.
